Josh's Prototype Javascript Relationship Editor
===============================================

version 1.0 - 10 March 2013
Copyright (c) 2013 Joshua Hawcroft <dev@joshhawcroft.com>


Description
-----------

Implementation of a visual database relationship editor using HTML, Javascript and CSS.


Requirements
------------

The implementation currently assumes a standards-compliant browser with support for the latest CSS 3 and Javascript APIs.

In particular, it relies upon CSS 3 transform rotate, and on recent Javascript event handling APIs.

It may not work in older browsers or in Internet Explorer, yet.


Files
-----

The editor functionality is all encapsulated within jh-dbrelationeditor.js.

Other supporting files include:

*	jhtk-dragndrop.js
	Quick, light-weight drag and drop implementation
	
*	jhtk-linediv.js
	Mechanism to draw diagonal lines using only DIV elements

*	jh-dbrelationeditor.css
	Controls the colour and appearance of the editor.
	
*	API
	Description of each of the functions exposed by the editor (public interface)

*	README
	This file.

